    header
      p.attribution photos by #[a(href='#NEED_URL') Laura de Reynal]

    .block.block-header
      h1.
        Studying the Global Web
      hr
      p.larger.
        Across the world, technology is used by many kinds of people, in very different circumstances, and for a variety of purposes.
      p.
        Mozilla has studied, documented, and learned from the stories of over 600 real people in 22 communities in 7 countries and their relationship with technology in an effort to understand thte role of the Web in their economies, their communities, their work â€” their lives.

    mixin block-pair(location, description)
      .wrapper(id=location.toLowerCase())
        .block.block-image
        .block
          h2=location
          hr
          p=description
          a(href='').button.
            Read #{location} report

